{"tid":1430564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］政府派人加固焊實北角街邊欄杆","createTime":"2019-08-07T18:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:04:07.000Z","uid":38386,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"09f637ca7b45ec94425ac8a8a36403055bf8a64d","tid":1430564,"uid":38386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:47:03.000Z","msg":"8-8 0240<br />\n北角香港殯儀館對外電車站旁鐵欄<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CRMvEab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCRMvEab.png&h=65333cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gor7Gox.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGor7Gox.png&h=6cfd77e1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmLz5Qe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmLz5Qe.png&h=608aaa30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影得好差因爲架小巴郁緊<br />\n<br />\n但明顯見到係路政署既人喺度將鐵欄既螺絲位焊實佢<br />\n<br />\n等我地到到星期日既港島東遊行既時候<br />\n<br />\n拆唔到街邊既欄杆<br />\n<br />\n前線勇武少左一層防線 防禦力大大受到影響<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各位夢遊者注意政府做緊小動作削弱緊我地前線既力量，相信唔止係北角整緊，SSP都有可能焊實左</span></span><br />\n<br />\nBe water, Be humble my friend<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"fc2de70fb7a3f9d5267a31e134351150041bddf1","tid":1430564,"uid":38386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:50:05.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"f2965ca95c26e347372a5e597a23e1b8664960e2","tid":1430564,"uid":38386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:58:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6a6b1a68ce2a3419ca87ed6c482c68ca9744c4a","tid":1430564,"uid":38386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:07:52.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"23459597b19b025e1371d3cbf8df5de39de3bd4c","tid":1430564,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:15:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21372e18f27e85fd6af4adc8130bc929fa53074b","tid":1430564,"ui